\033[1m\033[32mINIT\033[0m - Initialize a new mango repository

\033[1mUSAGE:\033[0m
    mango @init [repo_path] (-t, --template [template_name])

\033[1mDESCRIPTION:\033[0m
    Creates a new mango repository at the specified path using the given template.
    If no path is provided, initializes in the current directory.
    Default template is 'default'.

\033[1mARGUMENTS:\033[0m
    repo_path    Path where to create the repo (default: current directory)

\033[1mOPTIONS:\033[0m
    -t, --template    Template to use for initialization (default: default)

\033[1mEXAMPLES:\033[0m
    mango @init
    mango @init ~/my-project
    mango @init ~/my-project -t python